org.midao.core
Class MidaoTypes

java.lang.Object
  org.midao.core.MidaoTypes

public class MidaoTypes
extends java.lang.Object

Internal Types implementation to avoid dependency on JDBC version and allow compile under both Java 5 and 6. Please be aware that Types.ROWID, Types.NCHAR, Types.NVARCHAR, Types.LONGNVARCHAR, Types.NCLOB, Types.SQLXML would be supported only by Java 6 (JDBC 4.0) and should not be invoked during work with Java 5 (JDBC 3.0).
